Class Coupon

  • java.lang.Object
    • c_coupon.sys.core.beans.Coupon

  • public class Coupon
extends java.lang.Object

    Coupon class creates a new Coupon entity

    Purpose: creates a new Coupon entity, which will be used , later on

    When the Application will use DAO level to translate it to SQL and JDBC.
